conomic benefits with farreaching influence page contentacross our  countries of operations over  people work in a truly integrated way to find and produce oil and natural gas our technical capabilities asset quality and scale and financial strength are unmatched among independent exploration and production companies and uniquely position us to compete around the world conocophillips is committed to the efficient and effective exploration and production of oil and natural gas producing oil and natural gas and getting them to market takes ingenuity technology and investment our innovative collaborative efforts yield products that improve quality of life globally while producing economic benefits with farreaching influence​ our company an independent exploration and production company   fact sheets explore company assets operations and locations      spirit magazine the bakken resilient through industry cycles   our legacy the foundation for our operations        conocophillips company all rights reserved legal  privacy         us lower  go › us alaska go › canada go › colombia go › uk go › norway go › qatar go › malaysia go › indonesia go › china go › australia go › timorleste go › brunei go › libya go › global go › x worldwide operations select a location us lower  us alaska canada colombia uk norway qatar malaysia indonesia china australia timorleste brunei libya global phillips  nothing protects like shield™ introducing shield™ motor oil our new full line of automotive oils has seven unique formulations to provide car owners with the confidence and protection they need available products include premium full synthetic synthetic blend and conventional motor oils introducing shield™ motor oil our new full line of automotive oils has seven unique formulations view the full lineup guardol ect® diesel engine oil with liquid titanium® megaplex® xd triton® ell multiplex® red powerdrive® synthetic all season to fluid diamond class® turbine oil triton® synthetic transoil  